loss dead salvation~
   What is before you, is nothing new to this world, just a side of it most
people chose not to acknowledge.  It is the direct result of an ongoing
massacre of non-believers.  Those who chose to worship anything other than the
one true god are raped, robbed, and murdered, then dumped in this forsaken
pit.  The souls of these poor dead bastards scream out to be avenged.  The
center mass of the pile of naked, bloody, swollen, and mutilated corpses seems
to pulsate.  You hear something moaning, maybe you should enter and
investigate?  Maybe you shouldn't..  
~
